512
00:20:49,666 --> 00:20:50,833
[MAN]
Thanks for your purchase.

513
00:20:50,916 --> 00:20:52,166
I hope you enjoy it!

514
00:20:53,750 --> 00:20:54,708
[NOZOMI]
I can't believe

515
00:20:54,791 --> 00:20:55,708
it's night already!

516
00:20:55,791 --> 00:20:57,208
"Capital punishment."

517
00:20:57,291 --> 00:20:59,250
Do you really think
they'll execute us?

518
00:20:59,333 --> 00:21:01,375
But that would be
ridiculous, wouldn't it?

519
00:21:01,458 --> 00:21:03,041
I mean, just for
stealing a rock?

520
00:21:03,125 --> 00:21:05,041
Um, hello, we didn't
actually steal anything!

521
00:21:05,125 --> 00:21:06,416
Right, but we're dealing
with someone

522
00:21:06,500 --> 00:21:07,916
who doesn't believe
anything we say.

523
00:21:08,000 --> 00:21:08,958
That's the whole problem.

524
00:21:09,041 --> 00:21:10,750
Yeah, it's hopeless, isn't it?

525
00:21:12,583 --> 00:21:15,541
