the escaping part, at least,

539
00:21:37,333 --> 00:21:39,833
but they took our passports away
when they grabbed us.

540
00:21:39,916 --> 00:21:41,333
and we don't know
where our motorcycles are.

541
00:21:41,416 --> 00:21:42,958
Don't worry.
We'll figure it all out somehow.

542
00:21:43,041 --> 00:21:44,208
It doesn't work like that.

543
00:21:44,291 --> 00:21:45,500
[NOZOMI]
Besides, I don't want to

544
00:21:45,583 --> 00:21:47,458
run away when
we haven't done anything wrong.

545
00:21:47,541 --> 00:21:48,541
[AI]
I wasn't talking about

546
00:21:48,625 --> 00:21:49,791
running away.

547
00:21:49,875 --> 00:21:51,916
